{"tid":249982,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"肥婆減肥求督促指教","createTime":"2017-05-19T17:04:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-16T09:14:14.000Z","uid":87227,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6d3f41becfc0406cc31d502488cac5cb833a7e39","tid":249982,"uid":87227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T17:04:10.000Z","msg":"廿幾歲人肥到不似人形<br />\n想決心減肥又無恆心<br />\n希望有巴絲教路<br />\n得閒督促下我<br />\n成世人都冇瘦過<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66ed4fbf44e42b702b9559763e3ccb1a9515f171","tid":249982,"uid":78083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T17:05:56.000Z","msg":"試下切肉"},{"pid":"08a6e6a4d48bff0c053ab5d6b73ed297d3962895","tid":249982,"uid":87227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T17:08:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試下切肉</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/20/010751_db438822f32e316ad2f80afab99b5e5d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F20%2F010751_db438822f32e316ad2f80afab99b5e5d.jpg&h=05068377&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n應該可以食幾年"},{"pid":"a403a97bba9f1b862da6151232ea56e2ec130d82","tid":249982,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T17:08:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"87eb1680b73a2238bffd6ddf43c8c9d342815c39","tid":249982,"uid":87227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T17:20:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>死肥婆躝啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a055477e41cb9153dbca0825c347884503b84e53","tid":249982,"uid":113661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T17:24:41.000Z","msg":"人地有決心減肥你地咪支持下囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓豬我支持你架，大家努力啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61377dfde891e7fecd3db7641d95000fae1019d7","tid":249982,"uid":7992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T17:25:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 減肥戒煙一齊做"},{"pid":"889915ad4f3b3f71a9125a84eb40bebfefffbba1","tid":249982,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T17:40:29.000Z","msg":"屌 食個宵夜先啦"},{"pid":"6f6dd71a13fa8cc95ee94b17fa8b7136f1b12ece","tid":249982,"uid":83935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T17:47:20.000Z","msg":"有幾肥先你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d265bfa52eeed006e30765b9d6eee24cb4c449d8","tid":249982,"uid":87227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T17:49:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有幾肥先你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n加TG傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53dd79c9a4c5371540bf15df0a6e30a1224dbf3b","tid":249982,"uid":87227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T17:49:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人地有決心減肥你地咪支持下囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓豬我支持你架，大家努力啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f3675047ab3e70f8947d5ab5f383f5ee5e07d14","tid":249982,"uid":101074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T17:54:53.000Z","msg":"跑步？"},{"pid":"e64a125c16632eb7c2f735478492370128a9e019","tid":249982,"uid":87227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T18:16:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>跑步？</blockquote><br />\n腳都斷，腳痛呀我<br />\n游水好過"},{"pid":"ce31754a9cc0320a66d7f551af6d909ac03d78f8","tid":249982,"uid":77470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T18:57:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>跑步？</blockquote><br />\n腳都斷，腳痛呀我<br />\n游水好過</blockquote><br />\n你游水可唔可以keep到一星期游5日<br />\n每次30分鐘以上先<br />\n唔可以嘅話都係跑步，或者高強度間歇訓練啦<br />\n<br />\n我都肥仔黎，但用半年減左十幾公斤<br />\n就係靠跑同控制飲食<br />\n我第一日落街跑跑到腳底筋膜炎，成隻腳腫晒，結果之後二日跑唔到，去左游水，然之後都係選擇返跑<br />\n一開始慢慢跑，跑下停下<br />\n之後每次跑步距離嘅瓶頸都係腳痛同無氣之不斷轉換<br />\n之後耐久就越黎越長架喇<br />\n另外如果關節有任何痛，就等到好返晒先好跑<br />\n<br />\n飲食方面，首先要減零食，飲甜野<br />\n另外少食太油膩嘅野<br />\n並將一日三餐嘅間距控制得越短越好<br />\n<br />\n仲要就係要有充足睡眠"},{"pid":"cd71408fbc3e9afcdcbc499896d2ae98168a64a6","tid":249982,"uid":11876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T19:17:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>跑步？</blockquote><br />\n腳都斷，腳痛呀我<br />\n游水好過</blockquote><br />\n你游水可唔可以keep到一星期游5日<br />\n每次30分鐘以上先<br />\n唔可以嘅話都係跑步，或者高強度間歇訓練啦<br />\n<br />\n我都肥仔黎，但用半年減左十幾公斤<br />\n就係靠跑同控制飲食<br />\n我第一日落街跑跑到腳底筋膜炎，成隻腳腫晒，結果之後二日跑唔到，去左游水，然之後都係選擇返跑<br />\n一開始慢慢跑，跑下停下<br />\n之後每次跑步距離嘅瓶頸都係腳痛同無氣之不斷轉換<br />\n之後耐久就越黎越長架喇<br />\n另外如果關節有任何痛，就等到好返晒先好跑<br />\n<br />\n飲食方面，首先要減零食，飲甜野<br />\n另外少食太油膩嘅野<br />\n並將一日三餐嘅間距控制得越短越好<br />\n<br />\n仲要就係要有充足睡眠</blockquote><br />\n痴線跑步都做唔到既叫人做HIIT<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔洗一開波就游五日每次三十分鐘既<br />\n慢慢係加上去啦"},{"pid":"764164813ff7a089756b9b8d2967e0313aa58100","tid":249982,"uid":18923,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T10:31:22.000Z","msg":"唔係話打擊你，我真係未見過有肥婆上網搵人一齊減肥係會成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53fa938086084d57fad1dd96e53faafe01d6cdeb","tid":249982,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T10:32:28.000Z","msg":"有冇group"},{"pid":"2f8aa55571c18bb5cdfc71dcd53d40b2c68fcd25","tid":249982,"uid":33154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T23:26:19.000Z","msg":"我都減緊肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n共勉之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cbf14f0b9b487435e7f0e2fce71bb75afad9dcc","tid":249982,"uid":78118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T06:53:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"34db008647d3a9a222c4f68fa928439d5ead931a","tid":249982,"uid":120945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T15:32:35.000Z","msg":"食營養餐配合餐單<br />\n乖乖哋跟住餐單唔食立雜野可以減得好快😛"},{"pid":"2102567d68b418b36f022c22aa4e2f329d4925ab","tid":249982,"uid":73489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T08:32:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/Edith1992\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FEdith1992&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5ClnU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=a0b9120c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Edith1992</a>"},{"pid":"a534a4d9f49ebd702aff00758f779359221aff87","tid":249982,"uid":75394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T08:35:10.000Z","msg":"幾高幾多磅？？"},{"pid":"a1e39d8ed9e03be396ea5cad6ac211e49ac5bf53","tid":249982,"uid":12263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T08:36:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食營養餐配合餐單<br />\n乖乖哋跟住餐單唔食立雜野可以減得好快😛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有咩餐單分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a3d99a8c500036c8a99469aa6fcc3ce01f6aa91","tid":249982,"uid":67069,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T08:52:35.000Z","msg":"Me 53減到去46kg，目標43kg，幾年之間發現對我自己最有用既方法係食少d野，唔好運動咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食少d唔係指淨係食個蘋果定麥皮果d，我自己好少機會係屋企食飯，9成都係出街食，盡量唔食熱氣野，食飯既份量只比自己食半個飯以內，少食肉，唔飲汽水（/全部樽裝加工飲品）同唔食糖/甜品，零食都盡量少食，三餐之間餓就勁飲水。<br />\n<br />\n我就係發現越多運動個人就越易餓，食飯果時唔覺唔覺就食多左，結果就係肥肉加肌肉一樣增長，同目標越黎越遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9839665e4b156aad7c01864d4976dfb7716522c","tid":249982,"uid":62830,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T09:07:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Me 53減到去46kg，目標43kg，幾年之間發現對我自己最有用既方法係食少d野，唔好運動咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食少d唔係指淨係食個蘋果定麥皮果d，我自己好少機會係屋企食飯，9成都係出街食，盡量唔食熱氣野，食飯既份量只比自己食半個飯以內，少食肉，唔飲汽水（/全部樽裝加工飲品）同唔食糖/甜品，零食都盡量少食，三餐之間餓就勁飲水。<br />\n<br />\n我就係發現越多運動個人就越易餓，食飯果時唔覺唔覺就食多左，結果就係肥肉加肌肉一樣增長，同目標越黎越遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔好亂教人啦<br />\n鬼唔知唔食就會瘦咩，但係呢個方法會再減低自己嘅新陳代謝，你年紀再大啲身體會更差"}]}